174 A.3d 517 STATE OF NEW JERSEY, PLAINTIFF-RESPONDENT, v. BRIAN E. KILLION, DEFENDANT-PETITIONER.

C-163 September Term 2017

079355 October 16, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005025-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
